With this plugin, you can simply search by image to find similar products with lower prices and higher sales.
For each product, this plugin provides:
â¡ï¸ Product overview: Includes basic information such as sales, sales volume, and listing time.
â¡ï¸ Bulk download of product images: Includes main images, specifications, and descriptions.
